Configure NewCool Atlas browser to open planet.newcool.io on startup:
- Set homepage to https://planet.newcool.io
- Set startup URL to https://planet.newcool.io
- Set first run tab to https://planet.newcool.io/welcome
- Enable home button in toolbar
- Disable new tab page as homepage

